      Parameters:
      barcodeData - Object representing ASCII data of scanned barcode.
      barcodeType - Barcode type of the scanned barcode. Values of bar code data types are available in Table 3-6 of the Motorola Scanner SDK For Windows Developerâ€™s Guide (72E-149784-02).
      fromScannerID - Unique identifier of a particular active scanner assigned by SDK.
